parameters: Welcome to Double Dome Theater, how can I help you?
<Let’s see if I can spice things
up once we’re in the theater...>
Hello and welcome to Double Dome Pictures...
Hello. We would like two tickets for Love & Lilacs.
Sorry Ma’am, but we're no longer showing that film.
It was pulled due to poor performance.
Poor perf- You’re kidding me! I’ve been
waiting for this film for weeks now!
Then you could have seen it... Last week..?
Now what are we supposed to do?
Go home, and stream a movie like a normal person?
We would love to know what else is currently playing.
How should I know? I’m stuck here, in this ticket booth...
God I hate my life. I wasted so much money on film school...
Okay then... We’ll just be over here,
Espectra The Movie is going to be packed,
maybe a horror flick like Body Shop?
No one wants to read my screenplay...
I think I’m watching a horror movie right now.
Just pick something, anything, so we can get away from him.
I completely forgot this was coming out!
You know, the Triple Risk action saga starring Rand Risk.
“He’s ex-CIA, ex-special forces, and he’s the new cop
in town playing EX-ECUTIONER” and then he just starts
Look, there’s even a beautiful woman in
his arms right there on the poster.
That could be romance in the making.
But I haven’t even seen the first one.
This says Triple Risk TWO right on the title...
Actually it’s a sequel to a prequel which
technically is the sixth film in the series...
Stop talking. *Sigh*... I’m certain I’ll figure it out,
we don’t have any other options. Doubt there’s much
You heard the man, two tickets to Triple Risk.
By the way, would either of you be interested in
starring in an independent film project?
And we’re walking! We’re walking away, finding our seats!
<Nice one. You’ve really outdone yourself this time...>
<Thanks to your shitty attitude, he’s already regretting
the second date. Your mother was right, might as well buy
a dozen cats now because you’re poison to men everywhere!>
<Why am I even stressing over this - Him?!
This is supposed to be about your book! Not...>
COULD I GET SOME SERVICE HERE, PLEASE?!
Why does it... Are you the only one working here?..
could you please do something about that?
And if it isn’t too much trouble for an
obviously overtaxed individual such as yourself,
some popcorn would be nice as well.
Dammit, again? One second, I’ll go get the
broom and whack it a few times...
Here you are, Ma’am. We’re sorry for the inconvenience.
Help yourself to a free snack courtesy of Double Dome...
It’s popcorn, lady. We have a ton of it...
I’ll just be returning to my seat, then...
